      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以OnPremLinux是个子图，里面包含NFS节点，NFS的标签显示为FinTech_AuthVault对吗？另外AzCopy是独立在外部的工具？",
      "elements_involved": [
