      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，AzCopy部署在云端，用来和本地NFS做文件同步。还有个Files节点，代表LedgerService产生的业务文件流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AzCopy",
        "Files",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把子图画出来：OnPremLinux作为子图容器，内部放NFS节点。然后AzCopy放在子图外面，和NFS建立连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremLinux",
        "NFS",
        "AzCopy",
        "subgraph"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，我漏了一个监控节点。需要加个Note，标注这是FinTech_FraudDetection的审计入口，放在图下方比较醒目。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Note",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，Note节点放在底部，标签用FinTech_FraudDetection。现在确认下连线：AzCopy到Files是一条线，NFS到AzCopy是另一条，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AzCopy",
        "Files",
        "NFS",
        "wchart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，方向反了。AzCopy是主动拉取方，所以应该是AzCopy指向Files，表示数据流向；NFS指向AzCopy，表示NFS作为数据源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AzCopy",
        "Files",
        "NFS"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正箭头方向：AzCopy -- Files，NFS -- AzCopy。这样符合数据从NFS经AzCopy同步到Files的流向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AzCopy",
        "Files",
        "NFS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再确认下节点命名——AzCopy和NFS都显示FinTech_AuthVault？这是故意的，表示它们都归属认证保险库组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AzCopy",
        "NFS",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，AzCopy节点标签是FinTech_AuthVault，NFS节点标签也是FinTech_AuthVault，虽然名字相同但位置不同，不会冲突。Note节点保持FinTech_FraudDetection。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AzCopy",
